{
  "stem": "27351.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So as I said, the moment they-- they said, 'Jew,' I-- I felt trapped.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I did not react anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the atmosphere was getting less friendly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And at that moment, the train conductor came to check the tickets.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a tall older man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He probably was not older, but this is the way he looked to me at that time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He's sized up the situation quickly, and he asked for the tickets in a very all official way and asked, what's going on here?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then one of these women said, oh, we have this-- this little Jewish girl who is trying to escape the Kikes from the Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this man looked at them [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and he told them, in so many words, that they have to mind their own business and that he knows quite a few things about them, too.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, they were smugglers, so they were vulnerable.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they knew that there are policemen and Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Smuggling was punished.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I cannot tell you how I felt about this man who really saved my life.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I never saw him again, but I remember exactly how he looked.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and I only spent one day outside of the ghetto during the war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Living outside of the ghetto was terrible.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Hundreds of people I paid with their deaths for, you know, being Jewish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "People were sold sometimes for a kilo of sugar or, a bottle of vodka.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "However, everyone who did survive on the other side of the ghetto, including myself during this one day, survived because people helped him.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So this has to be remembered.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were good Poles, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in my case, completely unknown to-- completely not friends, nobody, who knew me, just decent people.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
